Class Version

java.lang.Object
com.authlete.common.util.Version
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Version>
public class Version extends Object implements Comparable<Version>, Serializable
A class that represents a version number consisting of a major number, a minor number and a patch number.
Since:
3.54
